00:20:44.760 --> 00:20:50.510
OK, theories without
equations are an organization

00:20:50.510 --> 00:20:53.930
of words that are
clearly defined,

00:20:53.930 --> 00:20:58.760
that try to make
explicit what is often

00:20:58.760 --> 00:21:01.850
tacit, that is unspoken.

00:21:01.850 --> 00:21:04.880
And in social
science, our task is

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:11.210
to make explicit and
describable through systematic

00:21:11.210 --> 00:21:15.830
observations, through
transparent methods, what

00:21:15.830 --> 00:21:17.850
