00:22:10.280 --> 00:22:12.020
that people give.

00:22:12.020 --> 00:22:17.510
So one pattern is the
psychological one,

00:22:17.510 --> 00:22:24.710
that people act on the basis
of individual desires, wills.

00:22:24.710 --> 00:22:28.700
That sometimes, this
