00:22:28.700 --> 00:22:32.240
is a product of
their DNA, nature,

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:36.020
they made their biography,
their parenthood.

00:22:36.020 --> 00:22:38.270
This is what made
them who there.

00:22:38.270 --> 00:22:40.740
There are different
