01:13:06.850 --> 01:13:08.650
that gas is really expensive.

01:13:08.650 --> 01:13:10.930
And this is also
environmentally friendly.

01:13:10.930 --> 01:13:11.820
But it's a lot of--

01:13:11.820 --> 01:13:13.810
people think that they're
going to save a lot of money.

01:13:13.810 --> 01:13:15.000
And if you show them the
numbers, they wouldn't.

01:13:15.000 --> 01:13:17.160
But whenever I
was getting a car,

01:13:17.160 --> 01:13:19.192
I was considering buying
a Prius, because it's

01:13:19.192 --> 01:13:20.650
environmentally
