01:14:26.640 --> 01:14:28.650
for efficiency.

01:14:28.650 --> 01:14:31.080
Why do people change
their clothes,

01:14:31.080 --> 01:14:33.300
change their hairstyles?

01:14:33.300 --> 01:14:36.270
It's not because it's
economically efficient.

01:14:36.270 --> 01:14:37.875
There is something else.

01:14:37.875 --> 01:14:42.060
PROFESSOR: Cadillac Escalades,
they don't carry much,

