01:15:45.710 --> 01:15:47.390
identified with.

01:15:47.390 --> 01:15:48.710
Come on.

01:15:48.710 --> 01:15:52.580
We wouldn't have the wars
we've been having if people all

01:15:52.580 --> 01:15:55.760
