01:15:55.760 --> 01:15:56.960
Think about it.

01:15:56.960 --> 01:15:59.750
Think what's driving the world.

01:15:59.750 --> 01:16:02.090
And the price of oil.

01:16:02.090 --> 01:16:08.150
Group identities, not rational
decision making, folks.

01:16:08.150 --> 01:16:11.030
It's group identities.

01:16:11.030 --> 01:16:15.320
Habitual, historic,
group identities

01:16:15.320 --> 01:16:19.400
have raised the price
of oil this week.

01:16:19.400 --> 01:16:22.970
Not rational decision making.

01:16:22.970 --> 01:16:25.820
The stock market
went down yesterday,

01:16:25.820 --> 01:16:27.500
