01:16:27.500 --> 01:16:30.650
Fear of oil reserves.

01:16:30.650 --> 01:16:33.050
The oil reserves did
not change yesterday.

01:16:36.110 --> 01:16:38.690
I am sorry to push back at you.

01:16:38.690 --> 01:16:40.370
Make the rest of the argument.

01:16:40.370 --> 01:16:41.420
Part of it's right.

01:16:41.420 --> 01:16:46.860
But those utilities
come from someplace.

01:16:46.860 --> 01:16:48.900
AUDIENCE: Yes, but what
I was trying to say

01:16:48.900 --> 01:16:54.610
is that I think
