01:17:14.833 --> 01:17:17.000
the savings they're going
to make and knowing that--

01:17:17.000 --> 01:17:18.375
SUSAN SILBEY: So
you want to do--

01:17:18.375 --> 01:17:21.250
OK, you want to do a
